        name - field that contains name of the set.

        comB - field that contains blue RGB value of main color of the set.
        bgR - field that contains red RGB value of background color of the window.
        bgG - field that contains green RGB value of background color of the window.
        bgB - field that contains blue RGB value of background color of the window.
        seR - field that contains red RGB value of secondary color of the set.
        seB - field that contains blue RGB value of secondary color of the set.
